'''加利·賀柏'''（{{lang-en|'''Gary Hooper'''}}，{{bd|1988年|1月26日|catIdx=Hooper, Gary}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[英式足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[錫周三足球會|錫周三]]。

==生平==
===球會===
;格雷斯
賀柏出生於[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]艾坪林（Epping Forest）的[[民政教區|民政教區]]朗頓（Loughton）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2009/mar/03/scouting-report-gary-hooper-scunthorpe-united |title=Scouting report: Gary Hooper, Scunthorpe United |publisher=[[衛報|''guardian.co.uk'']] |date=2009-03-03 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307015154/http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/blog/2009/mar/03/scouting-report-gary-hooper-scunthorpe-united |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，於2003/04年球季加盟當時仍處於[[英格蘭足球依斯米安聯賽|依斯米安聯賽]]超聯組（Isthmian Premier）的[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]，年僅15歲已獲派在「埃塞克斯郡高級盃」（Essex Senior Cup）對[[布倫特里鎮足球會|布倫特里]]（Braintree Town）時擔任沒有上場的後補球員。翌季格雷斯獲挑選加入新成立的[[英格蘭足球議會南部聯賽|議會南部聯賽]]，賀柏逐漸取得出場機會，在聯賽上陣29場並取得12個入球，協助球隊贏得首屆議會南部聯賽冠軍及升班到[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|議會全國聯賽]]，同時格雷斯亦晉級[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]決賽，在[[維拉公園球場|維拉公園球場]]對[[Hucknall_Town_F.C.|哈克纳尔城]]（Hucknall Town），正選上陣的賀柏在攔截對方的球員兼領隊迪恩·巴利克（Dean Barrick）時，引致對方懷疑斷腳而需由擔架抬離場，雙方在[[加時賽|加時賽]]後仍然1-1平手，賀柏在加時結束前被換離場，格雷斯在[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]於進入[[突然死亡|突然死亡]]後以6-5獲勝，成為[[雙料冠軍|雙料冠軍]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4570825.stm |title=Grays Ath 1-1 Hucknall Town (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-22 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2012-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111074324/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4570825.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2005/06年球季上半季賀柏與格雷斯同樣表現出色，於2005年11月26日對[[史提芬納治足球會|-{zh-hans:保罗夫史提芬;zh-hk:史提芬納治;}-]]射入個人第7球兼協助球隊重登榜首<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4449032.stm |title=Stevenage 0-1 Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-11-26 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307013808/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4449032.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但下半季狀態明顯下滑，僅在作客5-0大勝[[京达米士特足球俱乐部|京達米士特]]時多入1球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4842112.stm |title=Kidderminster 0-5 Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-03-28 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307213849/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/4842112.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。格雷斯最終以第3位結束球季，但在升班附加賽準決賽被[[Halifax_Town_F.C.|哈利法克斯]]（Halifax Town）淘汰，但球隊以2-0擊敗[[Woking_F.C.|沃金]]（Woking）成功衛冕[[英格蘭足總錦標|英格蘭足總錦標]]，賀柏在決賽擔任後備沒有被派上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thefa.com/TheFACup/FACompetitions/TheFATrophy/NewsAndFeatures/2006/FATrophyFinal_Report.aspx |title=Grays retain Trophy |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2006-05-14 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2011-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606164817/http://www.thefa.com/TheFACup/FACompetitions/TheFATrophy/NewsAndFeatures/2006/FATrophyFinal_Report.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季後領隊[[Mark_Stimson|馬克·史汀生]]（Mark Stimson）離隊，雖然賀柏上季在聯賽上陣37場及射入8球，仍然被新任領隊[[法蘭·格雷|法蘭·格雷]]（Frank Gray）中止合約棄用<small><ref name="Teenager Hooper">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/5177640.stm |title=Teenager Hooper released by Grays |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-13 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307124529/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/g/grays_athletic/5177640.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

;修安聯
賀柏以試訓球員身份為[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:巴尼特; zh-hk:班列特;}-]]在季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]上陣<small><ref name="Teenager Hooper"/></small>，其後參加[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]的試訓，於[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]2-1擊敗[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]射入致勝球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/5209452.stm |title=Hooper hopes to impress Shrimpers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-24 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2013-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013191739/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/5209452.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終獲時任領隊[[Steve_Tilson|史蒂夫·蒂尔森]]（Steve Tilson）給予一年合約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4780793.stm |title=Hooper signs deal with Shrimpers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-10 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2013-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013223809/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/4780793.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2006年8月22日在[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第一圈作客對[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伯恩茅斯; zh-hk:般尼茅夫;}-]]以後補身份首次為修安聯披甲上陣；10月24日在聯賽盃第三圈作客對[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]][[梅開二度|梅開二度]]，射入加盟以來的首兩個入球，協助球隊3-1獲勝晉級第四圈<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6072634.stm |title=Leeds 1-3 Southend |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-14 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2006-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061107185918/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6072634.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

但賀柏在聯賽僅獲派上陣18次，大部分以後補身份登場，只有3次正選上陣，沒有取得入球，季中以後更失去一隊席位，於2007年3月16日被外借到[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[莱顿东方足球俱乐部|奧連特]]直到球季結束，於首兩場賽事各入1球協助球隊賽和[[奥尔德姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:奥特汉姆; zh-hk:奧咸;}-]]及領頭羊[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6437239.stm |title=Leyton Orient 2-2 Oldham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=200-3-17 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2012-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114081734/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6437239.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6461669.stm |title=Leyton Orient 2-2 Scunthorpe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-24 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310075737/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6461669.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在上陣4場後，於5月2日被已確認降班的修安聯召回參賽對[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:南安普顿; zh-hk:修咸頓;}-]]的閉幕戰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6616237.stm |title=Shrimpers recall Hooper from loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-02 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2007-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071009122204/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6616237.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季後賀柏獲修安聯提供新約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6661025.stm |title=Hooper offered new Southend deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-16 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307150252/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6661025.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但他拒絕球會續約兩年的要求，而只願意續簽一年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6708971.stm |title=Southend shocked by Hooper U-turn |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-31 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306230056/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/6708971.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2007年10月13日主場3-0擊敗[[克鲁足球俱乐部|克魯]]，賀柏射入加盟以來首個聯賽入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7031416.stm |title=Southend 3-0 Crewe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-13 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2007-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014202809/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7031416.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；直到2008年1月20日作客4-1大勝[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:伯恩茅斯; zh-hk:般尼茅夫;}-]]才取得第2個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7184715.stm |title=Bournemouth 1-4 Southend |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-20 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2008-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121164056/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7184715.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。賀柏與修安聯加簽18個月新約留隊直到2009年6月後，於1月28日被外借到[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|赫里福特聯]]1個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7214128.stm |title=Hereford recruit Southend striker |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=208-1-28 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2008-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080203050044/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7214128.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。於上陣7場射入6球後，赫里福特聯延長借用至球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7257513.stm |title=Hooper extends Hereford loan deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-28 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307032253/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7257513.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。期間合共上陣19場及射入11球，於4月26日作客3-0擊敗[[布伦特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布伦特福德; zh-hk:賓福特;}-]]後確定直接升班[[英甲|英甲]]的資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7356090.stm |title=Brentford 0-3 Hereford |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-26 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2008-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080501084623/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7356090.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。賀柏返回修安聯在5月3日煞科日主戰1-1賽和已確定降班的[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:韦尔港; zh-hk:維爾港;}-]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7368708.stm |title=Southend 1-1 Port Vale |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-03 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2008-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080506082312/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7368708.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。修安聯以第6位的成績參加升班附加賽，準決賽兩回合累計1-5不敵[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:唐卡斯特; zh-hk:唐卡士打;}-]]出局，賀柏兩場均沒有入選出賽球員名單。球季結束後賀柏被掛牌求售，效力修安聯兩季上陣44次及射入4球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/7434233.stm |title=Hooper on Southend transfer list |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-03 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310122234/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/southend_utd/7434233.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在季末借用賀柏取得成功的[[靴尔福特联足球俱乐部|赫里福特聯]]向修安聯出價沒有獲得接納<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7487659.stm |title=Bulls still hope to land Hooper |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-03 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307230637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/hereford_united/7487659.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:切尔滕汉姆; zh-hk:車頓咸;}-]]出價雖然達到修安聯的目標，但賀柏拒絕加盟<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cheltenham_town/7500126.stm |title=Hooper turns down Cheltenham bid |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-10 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307194500/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cheltenham_town/7500126.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

