2008年7月14日賀柏正式加盟[[英甲|英甲]]球會[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯肯索普]]，轉會費初步為12.5萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，最終可增加至17.5萬英鎊，簽約三年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/7501669.stm |title=Striker Hooper joins Scunthorpe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-07-14 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628131010/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/7501669.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。8月9日聯賽揭幕戰主場對[[列斯聯足球會|-{zh-hans:利兹联; zh-hk:列斯聯;}-]]，賀柏為球隊先開紀錄，但最後被這隊升班大熱門反勝2-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541057.stm |title=Scunthorpe 1-2 Leeds |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-09 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2008-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080810030548/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7541057.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；8月30日作客3-0大勝升班馬[[斯托克港足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯托克港; zh-hk:史托港;}-]]賀柏[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7578359.stm |title=Stockport 0-3 Scunthorpe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-08-30 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308185530/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7578359.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；9月6日作客4-1擊敗[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布莱顿; zh-hk:白禮頓;}-]]更首次演出[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7588583.stm |title=Brighton 1-4 Scunthorpe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-06 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2014-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219083229/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7588583.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。10月18日作客2-1擊敗[[切尔滕汉姆足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:切尔滕汉姆; zh-hk:車頓咸;}-]]的入球是他加盟球隊首11場賽事射入第9球，斯肯索普史上僅次於[[比利·夏普|比利·夏普]]（Billy Sharp）的10球，他被[[傳媒|傳媒]]稱為「斯肯索普青年前鋒生產線」上最新出品<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/blog/2009/feb/02/scunthorpe-championship-football-league |title=Football League review: the 10-point guide to the weekend action |publisher=[[衛報|''guardian.co.uk'']] |date=2009-02-02 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2011-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110123233855/http://www.guardian.co.uk/sport/blog/2009/feb/02/scunthorpe-championship-football-league |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2009年4月5日斯肯索普晉級[[英格蘭聯賽錦標|英格蘭聯賽錦標]]決賽，在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]決戰[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]，賀柏雖然先拔頭籌，但最終於[[加時賽|加時賽]]以2-3落敗屈居亞軍<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7975143.stm |title=Luton 3-2 Scunthorpe (aet) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-05 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408040739/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7975143.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。加盟的首個球季賀柏合共射入30球，亦是僅次於比利·夏普的球會最高紀錄33球<small><ref name="Gary Hooper fitness">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Scunthorpe-sweat-on-Gary-Hooper-fitness-article26302.html |title=Scunthorpe sweat on Gary Hooper fitness |publisher=''mirrorfootball.co.uk'' |date=2009-05-21 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101108020406/http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Scunthorpe-sweat-on-Gary-Hooper-fitness-article26302.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>。斯肯索普以第6位的成績參加升班附加賽，雖然因傷缺席準決賽次回合，斯肯索普仍憑累計1-1，[[互射十二碼|互射十二碼]]7-6淘汰[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米爾頓凱恩斯]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038237.stm |title=MK Dons 0-0 Scunthorpe (agg 1-1) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-15 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090518043444/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/8038237.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。5月24日在[[溫布萊球場|溫布萊球場]]迎戰曾在聯賽兩勝的[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:米尔沃尔; zh-hk:米禾爾;}-]]，結果3-2獲勝取得升班[[英冠|英冠]]資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |title=Millwall 2-3 Scunthorpe |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-24 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090528171856/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8060955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年夏季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]結束前[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:女王公园巡游者; zh-hk:昆士柏流浪;}-]]曾出價100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]求購被拒<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/q/qpr/8232056.stm |title=Iron 'rejected' QPR's Hooper bid |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-01 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904063208/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/q/qpr/8232056.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。重返[[英冠|英冠]]的斯肯索普被視為降班熱門，但賀柏保持高效率入球數字，8月11日主場3-2擊敗[[德比郡足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:德比郡; zh-hk:打比郡;}-]]取得本季首兩個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8195031.stm |title=Scunthorpe 3-2 Derby |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-15 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2009-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817171917/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8195031.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後他再在[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]、[[沃特福德足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:沃特福德; zh-hk:屈福特;}-]]及[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:唐卡斯特; zh-hk:唐卡士打;}-]]身上[[梅開二度|梅開二度]]，及於2010年4月17日主場3-0擊敗[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:布里斯托尔城; zh-hk:布里斯托城;}-]]包辦三個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8616252.stm |title=Scunthorpe 3-0 Bristol City |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-17 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419234606/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8616252.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。4月20日賀柏射入1球協助球隊主場2-2賽和[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]，提早兩輪確定成功保級<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8620151.stm |title=Scunthorpe 2-2 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-20 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100423082233/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8620151.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。賀柏在[[斯肯索普2009年至2010年球季|2009/10年球季]]在聯賽射入19球，總計射入20球，再次成為球會首席射手，亦是[[英冠|英冠]]射手榜的三甲份子。

4月20日斯肯索普領隊[[尼祖·艾堅斯|尼祖·艾堅斯]]（Nigel Adkins）透露在夏季可能出售尚有一年合約的賀柏套現<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8631009.stm |title=Scunthorpe United ponder cashing in on Gary Hooper |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-20 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100503065703/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8631009.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。有報章報導[[蘇超|蘇超]][[老字號_(足球)|老字號]][[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]出價200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]求購，斯肯索普主席[[J._Steven_Wharton|史提夫·沃頓]]（Steve Wharton）否認其事，但承認有多支球隊表示興趣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8704043.stm |title=Scunthorpe United confirm bids made for Gary Hooper |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-25 |accessdate=2010-06-10 |archive-date=2010-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100531033812/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/scunthorpe_utd/8704043.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

;些路迪
在擾攘一段時間後，賀柏於2010年7月26日以240萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉投[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|些路迪]]，在通過體測後，他隨即飛赴[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]，與新隊友會合備戰[[2010/11賽季歐洲冠軍聯賽#外圍賽第三圈|歐聯外圍賽]]對[[布拉加體育會|布拉加]]的賽事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8852050.stm |title=Scunthorpe striker Gary Hooper signs for Celtic |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-07-27 |accessdate=2010-07-28 |archive-date=2010-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100728064124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/celtic/8852050.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他選擇穿著「88」號球衣，以紀念其出生年份1988年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://sport.stv.tv/football/scottish-premier/celtic/188621-hooper-to-wear-number-88-for-celtic |title=Hooper to wear number 88 for Celtic |publisher=''sport.stv.tv'' |date=2010-07-27 |accessdate=2010-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100730073749/http://sport.stv.tv/football/scottish-premier/celtic/188621-hooper-to-wear-number-88-for-celtic/ |archive-date=2010-07-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>。

;諾域治
2013年7月26日，[[英超|英超]]球會諾域治從[[蘇超|蘇超]]些路迪購入25歲前鋒賀柏，轉會費金額估計約500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，合約為期三年，另球會有選擇權延長多一年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23450297 |title=Gary Hooper: Celtic striker signs for Norwich City |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-07-26 |accessdate=2013-12-14 |archive-date=2013-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214095957/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/23450297 |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
2010年3月14日，年屆23歲的賀柏獲[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U21]]首次徵召，備戰月底對[[丹麥21歲以下國家足球隊|丹麥]]及[[冰島21歲以下國家足球隊|冰島]]兩場[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]，由於[[2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2011年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]的外圍賽展開時他仍未滿21歲，故此他仍合資格入選<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9424880.stm |title=Celtic's Gary Hooper called up for England Under-21s |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-14 |accessdate=2011-03-15 |archive-date=2011-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110316011033/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/9424880.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

